
                Layer 2 Discovery Module for LLDP
                      Introduction document
                      (Version 1.1, May 2019)

  What is it?
  -----------

  The LLDP monitoring module provides a function to read adjacent device 
  information of LLDP held by network equipment from Zabbix using SNMP.
  
  
  The Latest Version
  ------------------

  Details of the latest version can be found in the Zabbix Share.
  Open the download page under https://share.zabbix.com/network_devices/l2-discovery-module-for-lldp

  What are these files
  --------------------
  
  These files do not represent the full version of Layer 2 Discovery Module for LLDP, but instead the files that need to be modified within the main base project for it to be compatible with zabbix-map. Layer 2 Discovery Module for LLDP is a prerequisite for zabbix-map to work.
  
  Licensing
  ---------

  Please see the file called COPYING.


  Installation
  ------------
  
  Please download the full copy of Layer 2 Discovery Module for LLDP and read the instructions therein.

